  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Uriah's second stop will come this week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Agriculture, the second ship with 21,000 metric tons of urea fertilizers provided to Sri Lanka under the Indian loan scheme is scheduled to reach the port of Colombo this week.",
        "Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera said that it has been decided to stock up the stock of fertilizers and urea fertilizers that have been distributed for the yala season and also for the cultivation of maize, tea and yams.",
        "Out of the 65,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer provided to Sri Lanka by the Government of India, 44,000 metric tons of the first consignment was received earlier."
      ],
